reviews.text: Good place to have quick bite. The food selection and payment options at screens are awesome to avoid long queue and look though all options before finalizing the order.
Shop Location near Apm mall Kwun Tong, very convenient to the MTR station. Ideal place for taking a quick bites and go.
The usual McDonald's at a very convenient location

The place shouldn't be called a fast food restaurant. There was a very long queue even with the ordering kiosks fully functional. I made my order at the kiosk and waited for more than 15mins! The kitchen looked like a warzone, people running around trying to resolve orders that they somehow messed up.
Convenience place and near APM
